extendedInfo.description: Explore and discover County Wicklow on the east coast of Ireland with a simple swipe of your finger. This app will help you discover the true history of ireland and explore the rich culture and many fascinating historical places that shaped it through the ages.Accurate locations, and information for over 600 unique points of interest including castles, beaches, hiking trails and monuments including the incredible Monastic settlements of Glendalough Valley.*Over 600 Points of Interest from County Wicklow with information and images.*Swipe your finger across the information page to navigate to the next/previous point of interest within a category.Watch out for updates as more points of interest are added regularly.
